---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About ByteLite - Pioneering Data Transformation & Compression Innovation"
  description="ByteLite revolutionizes data storage through quantum compression and bytescale reduction technology. Our mission: democratize advanced data transformation to enable limitless computational possibilities and beneficial AGI through Deep Kore Neural Recursion."
  keywords={["ByteLite mission", "data transformation company", "quantum compression innovation", "bytescale technology", "compression breakthrough", "Tash Broadwater", "data miniaturization pioneer", "neural recursion development", "compression technology leadership", "AGI development"]}
  schemaType="AboutPage"
>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Origin Story -->
      <div id="story" class="story-section">
        <h2>The HeartStrings Discovery</h2>
        <div class="story-content">
          <p class="lead">
            In 2024, while developing HeartStrings, an AI-powered dating platform still in active development, 
            founder Tash Broadwater encountered a fundamental challenge: AI models demanded excessive data 
            storage and computing resources, limiting innovation for independent developers.
          </p>
          
          <blockquote>
            "What if the problem isn't the AI‚Äîbut the way we represent information?"
          </blockquote>
          
          <p>
            This breakthrough insight led to ByteLite: a revolutionary compression algorithm that achieves 
            ratios previously thought impossible, transforming 1GB into just 15 bytes through recursive 
            mathematical operations. While HeartStrings continues its development journey, ByteLite has 
            evolved into a standalone technology ready to transform data storage globally.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission & Vision -->
      <div class="mission-section">
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>
            To democratize access to advanced computation by making data storage and transmission 
            virtually free, enabling innovation at every scale.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>
            A world where computational limitations no longer constrain human creativity, 
            where AGI serves humanity, and where technology amplifies our highest aspirations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Current Status -->
      <div class="status-section">
        <h2>Project Status</h2>
        <div class="status-grid">
          <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>ByteLite Compression</h3>
              <span class="status-badge ready">Nearly Ready</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              The core compression technology is finalized and patent-pending. We're completing 
              final optimizations and preparing the ByteLite Application Demo for public release. 
              Enterprise licensing discussions are underway with multiple Fortune 500 companies.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 95%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>Deep Kore AGI</h3>
              <span class="status-badge complete">Framework Complete</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Mathematical proofs are finalized and the complete implementation blueprint is ready. 
              The recursive compression mathematics have revealed pathways to true artificial general 
              intelligence. Due to dual-use implications, deployment follows strict ethical guidelines.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill deepkore" style="width: 100%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>HeartStrings</h3>
              <span class="status-badge development">In Development</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              The AI-powered dating platform that sparked ByteLite's discovery continues active 
              development. HeartStrings will be the first consumer application to leverage ByteLite's 
              compression technology for efficient AI model deployment.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill heartstrings" style="width: 60%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Deep Kore Philosophy -->
      <div class="philosophy-section">
        <h2>Deep Kore Neural Recursion</h2>
        <p class="philosophy-intro">
          ByteLite's compression mathematics revealed unexpected patterns in information processing, 
          leading to breakthroughs in neural architecture design. With mathematical proofs complete 
          and implementation blueprints finalized, Deep Kore represents the next evolution in 
          artificial general intelligence.
        </p>
        
        <div class="philosophy-principles">
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">üåø</span>
            <h4>Efficient Intelligence</h4>
            <p>Doing more with less‚Äîtransforming constraints into capabilities</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">üåä</span>
            <h4>Recursive Depth</h4>
            <p>Learning through layers of mathematical transformation</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">‚ôæÔ∏è</span>
            <h4>Limitless Potential</h4>
            <p>Approaching theoretical infinity through innovation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder -->
      <div class="founder-section">
        <h2>Leadership</h2>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <h3>Tash Broadwater, Founder & CEO</h3>
          <p>
            Compression researcher and software engineer with 15+ years optimizing data systems. 
            Specializes in algorithmic design and edge AI systems. When traditional solutions fail, 
            Tash builds new ones from scratch‚ÄîByteLite is the result of that ethos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h3>Join Our Journey</h3>
        <p>Be part of the compression revolution and the path to beneficial AGI.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe for Updates</a>
          <a href="/licensing" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Licensing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .story-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .story-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  /* Status Section */
  .status-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .status-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .status-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .status-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .status-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .status-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .status-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .status-badge {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .status-badge.ready {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .status-badge.complete {
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2);
    color: #A855F7;
    border: 1px solid #A855F7;
  }

  .status-badge.development {
    background: rgba(255, 171, 0, 0.2);
    color: #FFAB00;
    border: 1px solid #FFAB00;
  }

  .status-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    height: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), #00A8CC);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .progress-fill.deepkore {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #A855F7, #FF006E);
  }

  .progress-fill.heartstrings {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF006E, #FFAB00);
  }

  .progress-fill::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3),
      transparent
    );
    animation: shimmer 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(-100%);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(100%);
    }
  }

  .mission-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .mission-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Philosophy Section */
  .philosophy-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .philosophy-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.5);
  }

  .philosophy-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .philosophy-principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .principle {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .principle .icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .principle h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .principle p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  /* Founder Section */
  .founder-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .founder-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .founder-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .founder-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #00B8E6;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-section h2,
    .status-section h2,
    .philosophy-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .status-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .status-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .philosophy-section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>